::Kilfest::

Killfest chuckles. As far as he could remember, Star Treck was a 
human show about space, aired somewhere in the 20th and sucseeding 
centuries. It was actually pretty good.

He turns his head to look at DarkMouse as she speaks up.

"Ok, I got all the bots on our team put on friendly by the defences," 
she says, tapping rapidly on the keyboard.
